\begin_inset Formula $H$
\end_inset

 types are more efficient, make more money 
\begin_inset Formula $h>l$
\end_inset

.
 Also probably 
\begin_inset Formula $y_{H}=h$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $y_{L}=l$
\end_inset


\end_layout

