\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
What should the government do?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
With no rules the bureaucrats choose the auction mechanism.
 Terrible!
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Government could set rules to be the testing + auction mechanism.
 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Bureaucrats with low 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma$
\end_inset

 break rules and use the auction mechanism.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Government could set rules to be the lottery
\end_layout

