\begin_layout Itemize
Bureaucrats make more money 
\begin_inset Formula $\rightarrow$
\end_inset

 smaller incentive to deviate
\begin_inset Formula $\rightarrow$
\end_inset

 fewer bureaucrats give all slots to 
\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

s
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
