\emph on
The bonus payment in the mission-oriented sector is
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
b_{11}^{*}=b_{22}^{*}=\tfrac{1}{2}\max\left\{ \max\left\{ \bar{\theta},\hat{\pi}\right\} ,\pi_{0}+\sqrt{\pi_{0}^{2}-4\underline{w}}-\bar{\theta}\right\} 
\]

\end_inset

and the bonus payment in the profit-oriented sector is
\begin_inset Formula 
