\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Play dictator game: At signup agents told that on-top of 40,000 ZMK show-up
 fee, they'll get 12,500 ZMK to donate to a well known HIV/AIDS charity
 or keep.
 Amount donated measures prosociality.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
We also expect different effects for high/low socio-economic status (utility
 is concave).
 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
